== INFRASTRUCTURE ==

Separate DB workflow (to avoid SQLite write lock contention):
  1. Crawlers accept --db flag to write to alternate database
  2. scripts/merge_db.py merges source DB into target (default: documents.db)
  3. Handles sites (upsert), categories (ID remap), documents (URL dedup)
  4. Does NOT merge citations, subsidy_items, document_changes

